title: Beyond the Horror: Asylum Episode 5
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: Love watching your weekly livestreams! I would have to say that Murder House is one of my favorite seasons because it was such a simple season and wasn't too complex, over the top, confusing storylines. But I have only seen the season once. Asylum is just okay to be it didn't motivate me to have to watch episode after episode like Murder House did! My favorite seasons are Coven, Murder House, Hotel, Roanoke, Asylum, and Freak Show. Please shout me out! I can't wait to see the new season of AHS! I also have a YouTube show that will be getting updated very soon. Thanks in advance.
